Other top selling items from the auction were a straw hat worn by Leigh that sold for $52,500.

The Kenosha Professional Police Association claims the billboard is simply to thank the local community for its support. Torres shot another man 10 days before Siler killing.

Rebbie said that he purchased the camera specifically to watch the 15-year-old girl but captured other victims on film, too. Rebbie's  is being held on a $500,000 bail and will appear in court on May 1.
